quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,80,Futhi ngempela izihlali zase-Hijr zaziphika izithunywa
  15,81,Futhi sabanikeza izimpawu zethu kepha abazinakanga (bazifulathela)
  15,82,Futhi babeqopha izintaba ukuze bakhe izindlu (bazizwe) bephephile
  15,83,Ngakho-ke umsindo owesabekayo wabathatha ngesikhathi sasekuseni
  15,84,Ngakho-ke akubazuzelanga lutho lokho ababekusebenzela
  15,85,Futhi asizange siwadale amazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ngaphandle kweqiniso futhi ngempela ihora liyeza ngakho-ke thethelela ngentethelelo emnene
  15,86,Ngempela iNkosi yakho ingumdali (wamazulu nomhlaba) iyisazi
  15,87,Futhi ngempela sikunikezile (amavesi) ayisikhombisa aphindaphindiwe (Surah Fatiha) kanye neQur’an enkulu (engcwele)
  15,88,Ungaphonsi amehlo akho kulokho esikuphe abanye phakathi kwabo njengesipho ukuze bazitike ngakho futhi ungabi lusizi ngabo yehlisela amaphiko akho (umusa wakho) phezu kwabakholwayo
  15,89,"Futhi uthi, “ngempela mina ngingumxwayisi ogqamile”"
  15,90,Njengoba sehlisa phezu kwalabo ababehlukanisa
  15,91,Labo abenza iQur’an ukuthi ibe izingxenye
  15,92,Ngakho-ke ngifunga ngeNkosi yakho! Siyobabuza bonke ndawonye
  15,93,Mayelana nalokho ababekwenza
  15,94,"Ngakho-ke\tmemezela\tngokusobala\tngalokho\tophoqwe ngakho futhi uqhelelane nabakhonzi bezithixo"
  15,95,Ngempela thina sikwenele ukubhekana nabenza inhlekisa
  15,96,Labo abenza omunye unkulunkulu (isithixo) basihlanganise noMvelinqangi ngakho-ke bayokwazi
  15,97,Futhi ngempela siyazi ukuthi wena siyacinana isifuba sakho ngenxa yalokho abakushoyo
  15,98,Ngakho-ke dumisa udumo lweNkosi yakho futhi ube ngomunye wabazithobayo
  15,99,Futhi khonza iNkosi yakho kuze kube ufikelwe isiqiniseko (ukufa)